Detailed Description

cvmx_ciu_pp_rst

This register contains the reset control for each core. A 1 holds a core in reset, 0 release from reset. It resets to all ones when REMOTE_BOOT is enabled or all ones excluding bit 0 when REMOTE_BOOT is disabled. Writes to this register should occur only if the CIU_PP_RST_PENDING register is cleared.
